org.kepler.gui

Class TabManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.gui.TabManager

  • public class TabManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This singleton class can be used to hold references to java components that implement the TabPane interface so they can be accessed and controlled from anywhere. Add methods to this class as you need them.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.awt.Color BGCOLOR
      Due to slight color change in the background area of a tab this color should be used to set the background color of components inside the tab.
